\c 50
\s Kuvigwa kwaJakove, nokufa kwaJosefa
\p
\v 1 Zvino Josefa wakawira pamusoro pechiso chababa vake, ndokuchema pamusoro pake, ndokumutsvoda.
\v 2 Josefa ndokuraira varanda vake n'anga kuomesa baba vake, n'anga ndokuomesa Israeri.
\v 3 Zvino mazuva makumi mana ndokuzadziswa kwaari, nokuti saizvozvo aizadziswa mazuva eavo vaiomeswa, nevaEgipita vakamuchema mazuva makumi manomwe.
\p
\v 4 Mazuva ekuchema kwake akati apfuura, Josefa akataura kuimba yaFarao, achiti: Ikozvino kana ndawana nyasha pameso enyu, taurai henyu munzeve dzaFarao, muchiti:
\v 5 Baba vangu vakandipikisa, vachiti: Tarirai, ndofa, muguva rangu randakazvicherera munyika yeKenani ndimo mauchandiviga. Naizvozvo ikozvino, regai ndikwire hangu, ndindoviga baba vangu, ndogodzoka.
\p
\v 6 Farao ndokuti: Kwira, unoviga baba vako, sezvavakakupikisa.
\p
\v 7 Josefa ndokukwira kunoviga baba vake, nevaranda vose vaFarao vakakwira naye, vakuru veimba yake, nevakuru vose venyika yeEgipita,
\v 8 neimba yose yaJosefa, nevana vababa vake, neimba yababa vake; pwere dzavo dzoga, nemakwai avo, nemombe dzavo, vakasiya munyika yeGosheni.
\v 9 Zvino kwakakwira pamwe naye zvose ngoro nevatasvi vemabhiza, rikava boka guru-guru.
\p
\v 10 Zvino vakasvika paburiro raAtadhi, riri mhiri kwaJoridhani, ndokumuchemapo nekuchema kukuru kunorwadza kwazvo; vakaitira baba vake mariro mazuva manomwe.
\v 11 Zvino vaigara panyika iyo, vaKenani vakaona mariro paburiro raAtadhi, vakati: Awa mariro anorwadza kuvaEgipita; naizvozvo zita raro rakanzi Abherimiziraimi, iri mhiri kwaJoridhani.
\v 12 Zvino vanakomana vake vakamuitira sezvaakange avaraira;
\v 13 nokuti vanakomana vake vakamutakurira kunyika yeKenani, ndokumuviga mubako remunda weMakipera, riya Abhurahama raakatenga kuna Efuroni muHeti pamwe nemunda ive nzvimbo yake yekuviga, pakatarisana neMamure.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Josefa wakadzokera kuEgipita, iye nevana vababa vake, nevose vakakwira pamwe naye kunoviga baba vake.
\v 15 Vana vababa vaJosefa vakati vaona kuti baba vavo vakange vafa, vakati: Zvimwe Josefa achativenga, uye zvirokwazvo achatitsiva zvakaipa zvose zvatakaita kwaari.
\v 16 Zvino vakapa murairo kuna Josefa, vachiti: Baba vako vakaraira vasati vafa, vachiti:
\v 17 Muchataura seizvi kuna Josefa, muti: Dokanganwira hako kutadza kwevana vababa vako; nezvivi zvavo, nokuti vakakuitirai zvakaipa; zvino dokanganwirai kutadza kwavaranda vaMwari wababa venyu. Josefa akachema pakutaura kwavo naye.
\p
\v 18 Vakuru vake vakaendawo, vakawira pasi pamberi pake, vakati, Tarirai, tiri varanda venyu.
\p
\v 19 Josefa akati kwavari, Musatya, nokuti ini ndiri pachigaro chaMwari here?
\v 20 Kana murimwi, makandifungira zvakaipa, asi Mwari akafunga kuti zvive zvakanaka, kuti zviitwe sezvinoitwa nhasi, kuti vanhu vazhinji vararamiswe.
\v 21 Naizvozvo zvino musatya, ndichakuchengetai, nepwere dzenyu. Akavanyaradza, akataura navo nomoyo wakanaka.
\p
\v 22 Josefa akagara Egipita, iye naveimba yababa vake; Josefa akagara makore ane zana negumi.
\v 23 Josefa akaona vana vaEfuremu vorudzi rwechitatu, navana vaMakiri, mwanakomana waManase, vakaberekerwa pamabvi aJosefa.
\v 24 Josefa akati kuhama dzake, Ndofa, asi Mwari achakumutsai zvirokwazvo, nokukubudisai panyika ino, muende kunyika yaakapikira Abhurahama naIsaka, naJakove.
\v 25 Josefa akapikisa vana vaIsraeri, akati, Mwari achakumutsai zvirokwazvo, nemwi mutakure mafupa angu abve pano.
\v 26 Ipapo Josefa akafa, ava namakore ane zana negumi; vakamusasika, akaiswa mubhokisi paEgipita.
